text: Mattias Eriksson (born 17 November 1981 in Sundsvall, Medelpad) is a Swedish archer. He competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics and at the 2004 Summer Olympics.Mattias ErikssonMattias ERIKSSON ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish archers Category:Olympians for Sweden Category:Sportspeople from Sundsvall
